    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Lantana Commercial Discussion (05/05/2026)",
      "content": "June 2025 looked to amend directors, but nothing ever got adopted or recorded.\n\nBylaws / CCR's would need to be updated before we find new directors (if this is what we wanted to complete).\n\nShanta asked to dissolve commercial association - Forestar owns one certain parcel (northwest corner), and there are undeveloped commercial lots... Is FOR land under residential or commercial? Residential not run by FOR. **Answer** - If commercial does not own any land, or have not been collecting assessments, then it can be dissolved.\n\nWe can appoint a new board to put owners on the board and have us get out, or partially terminate (or assign) our declarant rights.\n\nWe can assign ARC / review rights to other people / members.\n\nStep 1) Amend and restate bylaws to appoint board\nStep 2) Update agent through Secretary of State\n\n",
      "folderId": 5,
      "created": "2026-05-05T19:00:36.263Z",
      "updated": "2026-05-05T19:29:34.068Z"
    },
